{"tid":2512970,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"巴菲特坦承後悔去年減持蘋果及航空股  稱讚Tim Cook領導蘋果更勝Steve Jobs","createTime":"2021-05-02T06:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T06:56:02.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5375717c277ba11c7f1f15605c15e85d3a61a338","tid":2512970,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:48:03.000Z","msg":"股神巴菲特（Warren Buffett）旗下波克夏海瑟威（BERKSHIRE HATHAWAY，以下稱波克夏）第1季營利增長20%，在周六的年度股東大會上，巴菲特坦承替去年減持蘋果公司（Apple Inc.）股票、拋售航空股的情形以及失敗的健康照護投資感到後悔。<br />\n<br />\n談到去年賣出一部分Apple股票的操作，巴菲特表示：「我去年賣了一些股票，雖然我們的股東仍因為我們回購股票而看到股價上漲，但這或許是個錯誤，」巴菲特提到，老搭檔孟格（Charlie Munger）也同樣認為巴菲特犯了錯。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n巴菲特稱讚Apple執行長庫克（Tim Cook）將Apple打理得非常好，並表示：「從創造力來看，他（庫克）無法做到像賈伯斯顯然能做到的一樣，但從許多方面來看，我不認為賈伯斯能做到庫克所達成的事情。」<br />\n<br />\n除了減持Apple股票外，外界質疑為何波克夏沒有在去年3月股市大跌時逢低買入，相反地卻在美國封鎖的第1周拋售航空股，之後又減持銀行股<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n不過他表示考慮到目前旅行上的壓力，他仍不會投資航空股。（陳韻婷／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210502/YAZI32K24JF4BLWLTNNKDKSIGM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210502%2FYAZI32K24JF4BLWLTNNKDKSIGM%2F&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNooeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=cae60bb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210502%2FYAZI32K24JF4BLWLTNNKDKSIGM%2F&h=180d33fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210502/YAZI32K24JF4BLWLTNNKDKSIGM/</a>"},{"pid":"b7d8c100261d70c22c357b3d69697f02b38e454a","tid":2512970,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:52:29.000Z","msg":"唔飲罐裝可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4e6bb55dc2ee1ca35579cb1cbc3b4795627c5c","tid":2512970,"uid":300630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:53:23.000Z","msg":"得連登仔仲日日Steve Jobs<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f568ce24dc5db4811309d22aad47ecf5e5a7b4","tid":2512970,"uid":261819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:55:00.000Z","msg":"不過他表示考慮到目前旅行上的壓力，他仍不會投資航空股<br />\n<br />\n有少少自相矛盾咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n姐係有貨既就sh到返家鄉，無貨既就唔建議買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b4a776ad5c71f2c46097ed94632b2a3dea3b45","tid":2512970,"uid":36567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:56:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTim Cock點勁法<br />\n廢老真係廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}